\zeta(n)
n
n
 \zeta(n) = \sum_{k \ge 1} \frac 1{k^n} = \sum_{k \ge 1} \prod_{p^{k_p} || k} \frac 1{(p^n)^{k_p} } = \prod_{p} \sum_{k \ge 0} \left( \frac 1{p^n} \right)^k = \prod_{p} \frac 1{1-\frac 1{p^n}}. 
